@startuml
' Product: Mentat
' URL: https://www.mentat.ai/

package "Mentat Architecture" {
    [Conversation Manager] as MGR
    [Code Context] as CTX
    [LLM API] as API
    [Git Interface] as GIT
    [Parser/Diff Engine] as DIFF
}

MGR --> CTX : "Prune Context (Token Limit)"
MGR --> API : "Stream Response"
MGR --> GIT : "Apply Changes"
CTX --> DIFF : "Parse/Rank Files"

note right of MGR
  Dynamically prunes context
  based on token limits.
end note
@enduml
